alexis p michas  juniper investment company juniper investment company alexis p michas mr michas has been the managing partner of juniper since its inception he was the managing partner of stonington partners a private equity firm with over  billion in assets from  from  to  he helped to build merrill lynch capital partners into the leading wall streetaffiliated private equity firm assuming management responsibility in  and negotiating the transition that enabled the formation of stonington partners he has been involved in more than  significant purchase or sale transactions  ipo’s and a multitude of private and public financings recapitalizations and spinoffs he has negotiated and managed over  billion of realizations from investments in notable marketleading companies including blue bird borgwarner burns international eckerd esstar lincoln educational services packard bioscience company and perkinelmer mr michas received his ba from harvard university and his mba from harvard business school he is chairman of the board of directors of borgwarner inc a director of perkinelmer inc and allied motion technologies inc and has previously served on the boards of airtran airways inc burns international eckerd corporation lincoln educational services corporation and packard bioscience company juniper teamalexis p michas john a bartholdson       james e fayal bradley j hoecker nassos michas cfa edward c reeves       nicos k anastasopoulos alexis michas  leadership  about us  company  perkinelmer corporate lab products  services contact us welcome loginregister toggle navigation alexis p michas managing partner juniper investment company llc mr michas has been managing partner of juniper investment company llc since he founded the firm in  juniper is also a principal of aetolian investors llc a registered commodity pool operator mr michas was the managing partner and a director of stonington partners inc an investment management firm from  to  prior to that mr michas was a p